Ultimo took a step back "Energy Barrette"

"Online"

A long barrette of pure energy so condense it made a solid able to change in shape.  Ultimo hit the sabre to the side then parried by having the  barrette extend towards Hellpeons sword hand.  With his other hand he threw  his shield in front of the blast but it knocked him back a bit from the close range, also obscurring the attack of his barrete causing Ultimo to swing his arm up the extended barrette going straight at Hellpeons neck from the chest area.
